It's the 5th happiest country according to the World Happiness Report. She has a job waiting, a gorgeous flat for the pair of them, and I love her husband and know he'll be extraordinarily good to her.

But she'll be so far away. I don't know what I'm gonna do without my Monkey.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NYRaHvw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hahway]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Part II + Bonus...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UbmlIgr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xTakBap.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Part I</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/14pXdhf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Part II</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3H8TP6f.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bonus I</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xYR2rHL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bonus II</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UbmlIgr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MauroChanique]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I’ve made my choice</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9qU5LJh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rLcH50P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9qU5LJh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LimJahey504]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sugar pulling machine</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IjPmWng</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/USPVxKz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IjPmWng</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HotCoffee9520]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Family first</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QS8SPWR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VwfzNmn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QS8SPWR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vtrv